# Styling Guidelines

## SCSS Modules

Component-scoped styling. File `component-name.module.scss` MUST be in the same directory as the component.

```
component/
├── component-name.tsx
├── component-name.module.scss  ✓
└── component-name-logic-layer.tsx
```

## Imports

**TS/TSX importing `.module.scss` — use absolute path from `src/`, import as `classes`:**

```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT
import classes from 'src/features/feature-name/ui/component-name.module.scss';

// ❌ WRONG
import classes from './component-name.module.scss';
```

**SCSS internal imports (@use) — absolute path from `src/`:**

```scss
// ✅ CORRECT
@use 'src/shared/ui/styles/themes.scss';

// ❌ WRONG
@use './themes.scss';
```

**Variables:** Auto-imported via Vite. Do NOT manually import `variables.scss`.

## Class Naming

Use **camelCase** in `.module.scss`:

```scss
// ✅ CORRECT
.container { }
.primaryButton { }
.cardHeader { }

// ❌ WRONG
.primary-button { }
```

## Variables

See `src/shared/ui/styles/variables.scss`: `$spacing-*`, `$primary-color`, `$radius-*`, `$shadow-*`, `$font-size-*`, etc.

## Patterns

- **Nesting:** `&:hover`, `&.modifier`, `&Header` (BEM-like)
- **Multiple classes:** use template literals with `classes.button`, `classes.primary`
- **Conditional:** `isActive ? classes.active : ''` inside template literal
- **Responsive:** `@media (min-width: 768px)` in SCSS
- **Layout:** Flexbox (`display: flex`, `gap`) or Grid (`grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr))`)
- **Transitions:** `transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out`
- **Z-index:** Define `$z-modal`, `$z-dropdown` in variables

No inline styles. Global styles only in `src/shared/ui/styles/global.scss`.

## Shared UI

Components in `src/shared/ui/` must have their own `.module.scss` and be reusable.
